en_150425_1	This new Course saw its birth as a conceptual notion of the Commander of the Army, Lieutenant General Mahesh Senanayake in the recent past and turned popular among Officers.
en_150425_2	Accordingly, 44 Officers serving in all formations under the SFHQ-J followed the Course on the instructions of Major General Dharshana Hettiarrachchi, Commander, Security Forces - Jaffna.
en_150425_3	The closing certificate awarding ceremony took place at the SFHQ-J auditorium in the presence of Major General Roshan Seneviratne, General Officer Commanding, 51 Division who attended as the Chief Guest.
en_150425_4	Directorate of Training facilitated the supply of external resource personnel for lectures to the Course attendees.
en_150425_5	Senior Officers at the SFHQ-J, several invitees and Course attendees were present during the brief closing ceremony.
